    java.lang.Comparable<AbstractSegmentHandlePart<? extends javafx.scene.Node>>, IActivatable, IAdaptable, IAdaptable.Bound<IViewer>, IDisposable, IHandlePart<HoverOverlayImageView>, IVisualPart<HoverOverlayImageView>
    public class HideHoverHandlePart
extends AbstractSegmentHandlePart<HoverOverlayImageView>
    The HideHoverHandlePart is an AbstractSegmentHandlePart that displays a "collapse" image. By default, the HideFirstAnchorageOnClickHandler is installed for HideHoverHandlePart, so that the corresponding NodePart can be hidden by a click on this part.
